net.fathomsoft.nova.tree

Class FileDeclaration

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.fathomsoft.nova.tree.Node
      • net.fathomsoft.nova.tree.FileDeclaration

  • public class FileDeclaration
extends Node
    Class used to organize the Files that are fed to the compiler. Each file has a file name that is stored in the name field variable of this class.
